<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>Healthy Living Education Alliance</title>

<style>

body{
font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
margin:0;
background:#f5f9fc;
color:#1c2b36;
}

.container{
max-width:1100px;
margin:auto;
padding:40px 20px;
}

header{
background:white;
border-bottom:1px solid #ddd;
}

nav{
display:flex;
justify-content:space-between;
align-items:center;
padding:15px 20px;
}

nav a{
margin-left:20px;
text-decoration:none;
color:#1c2b36;
font-weight:600;
}

.hero{
background:linear-gradient(120deg,#1f6fb2,#2ca56d);
color:white;
padding:80px 20px;
}

.hero h1{
font-size:42px;
margin-bottom:20px;
}

.hero p{
max-width:650px;
font-size:18px;
}

.button{
display:inline-block;
padding:12px 22px;
margin:15px 10px 0 0;
border-radius:30px;
text-decoration:none;
font-weight:bold;
}

.primary{
background:#f39c2b;
color:white;
}

.secondary{
background:white;
color:#1f6fb2;
}

.section{
padding:70px 20px;
}

.grid{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));
gap:30px;
}

.card{
background:white;
padding:25px;
border-radius:10px;
box-shadow:0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
}

.card h3{
margin-top:0;
}

.blue{border-top:6px solid #1f6fb2}
.orange{border-top:6px solid #f39c2b}
.green{border-top:6px solid #2ca56d}
.yellow{border-top:6px solid #f4c542}

footer{
background:#1c2b36;
color:white;
padding:40px 20px;
text-align:center;
}

button.lang{
background:#f4c542;
border:none;
padding:8px 12px;
border-radius:5px;
cursor:pointer;
font-weight:bold;
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
<nav>

<strong>HLEA</strong>

<div>
<a href="#mission">Mission</a>
<a href="#programs">Programs</a>
<a href="#values">Values</a>
<a href="#team">Team</a>
<a href="#contact">Contact</a>
<button class="lang">Español</button>
</div>

</nav>
</header>

<section class="hero">

<div class="container">

<h1>Empowering Patients. Training Professionals. Optimizing Life.</h1>

<p>
Welcome to the Healthy Living Education Alliance (HLEA).  
At HLEA, we believe managing obesity and metabolic health requires more than advice—it requires a movement.
</p>

<p>
We are a nonprofit dedicated to bridging the gap between clinical science and everyday life.
Whether you are a patient seeking sustainable health tools or a healthcare provider pursuing advanced training in cardiovascular prevention and longevity, you’ve found your alliance.
</p>

<a class="button primary" href="#programs">Explore Our Programs</a>
<a class="button secondary" href="#providers">For Healthcare Providers</a>

</div>

</section>

<section class="section" id="mission">

<div class="container">

<h2>Our Purpose</h2>

<p>
The Healthy Living Education Alliance was founded to address the global challenge of metabolic disease.
Obesity is a complex condition that requires a dual approach: patient-centered education and specialized professional development.
</p>

<p>
Our mission is to translate cutting-edge clinical science into practical tools that empower individuals, healthcare providers, and communities to achieve sustainable health.
</p>

</div>

</section>

<section class="section">

<div class="container">

<h2>Our Strategic Pillars</h2>

<div class="grid">

<div class="card blue">
<h3>For Patients</h3>
<p>
We provide evidence-based education that removes stigma and replaces it with practical knowledge about nutrition, metabolic health, and sustainable lifestyle changes.
</p>
</div>

<div class="card green" id="providers">
<h3>For Professionals</h3>
<p>
We train healthcare providers in obesity management, cardiovascular prevention, and longevity science to improve patient outcomes and quality of care.
</p>
</div>

<div class="card orange">
<h3>For the Future</h3>
<p>
Through collaboration and education, we aim to expand prevention, improve healthcare delivery, and extend healthy lifespans.
</p>
</div>

</div>

</div>

</section>

<section class="section" id="values">

<div class="container">

<h2>HLEA Core Values</h2>

<div class="grid">

<div class="card blue">
<h3>Evidence-Based Integrity</h3>
<p>
Health education must be grounded in rigorous science and the latest clinical research.
</p>
</div>

<div class="card orange">
<h3>Radical Compassion</h3>
<p>
Obesity is a complex medical condition, not a character flaw. We remove stigma and foster empathy.
</p>
</div>

<div class="card green">
<h3>Proactive Longevity</h3>
<p>
Our focus is long-term health-span, preventing disease and optimizing vitality.
</p>
</div>

<div class="card yellow">
<h3>Educational Accessibility</h3>
<p>
We translate high-level medical insights into accessible knowledge for everyone.
</p>
</div>

<div class="card green">
<h3>Community-Centered Equity</h3>
<p>
We focus on underserved communities, particularly Hispanic and Spanish-speaking populations, ensuring equitable access to metabolic health education.
</p>
</div>

</div>

</div>

</section>

<section class="section" id="programs">

<div class="container">

<h2>Our Programs</h2>

<div class="grid">

<div class="card">
<h3>Community Health Workshops</h3>
<p>Education on nutrition, exercise, and metabolic health.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Chronic Disease Education</h3>
<p>Programs supporting individuals managing diabetes and cardiovascular disease.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Youth Wellness</h3>
<p>Early lifestyle education for younger populations.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Senior Health</h3>
<p>Programs supporting independence and healthy aging.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Workplace Wellness</h3>
<p>Helping organizations improve employee health and productivity.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Community Outreach</h3>
<p>Health fairs and public education events.</p>
</div>

</div>

</div>

</section>

<section class="section" id="team">

<div class="container">

<h2>Our Leadership</h2>

<div class="grid">

<div class="card">
<h3>Dr. Al William Robaina</h3>
<p>Founder, President, Head MD</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Chris Robaina</h3>
<p>VP and Head of Non-Clinical Staff</p>
<p>NBHWC Accredited Health Coach</p>
<p>National Diabetes Prevention Program Certified</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Sophia Idriss</h3>
<p>Head of Community Outreach and Social Media</p>
</div>

</div>

</div>

</section>

<section class="section" id="contact">

<div class="container">

<h2>Contact Us</h2>

<p>Email: contact@healthylivingalliance.org</p>

<p>
Questions about programs, partnerships, or volunteering? Reach out and connect with the HLEA team.
</p>

</div>

</section>

<footer>

<p>Healthy Living Education Alliance</p>
<p>Advancing health through education, outreach, and community programs.</p>

<p>© 2026 HLEA</p>

</footer>

</body>
</html>
